{"tid":2434404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝Ex 令自己成長","createTime":"2021-03-05T13:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T21:36:36.000Z","uid":384424,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"37af469b30b1b446d174da135a0ff449b97753c1","tid":2434404,"uid":384424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"大概一年前同你分左手<br />\n個陣我好唔明白 點解你會離開<br />\n以為呢個世界有愛就所有嘢都解決到<br />\n一開始唔理解 放唔低<br />\n但今年開始出黎社會做嘢<br />\n以前唔體諒你做嘢幾辛苦 成日發脾氣<br />\n開始慢慢發現你當初既難處 <br />\n以前以為係你問題 <br />\n（雖然係你出軌）<br />\n宜家識得反省原來自己都有問題<br />\n宜家我完全尊重你當初決定 <br />\n開始放低到 <br />\n多謝你令我明白更多嘢 <br />\n多謝你令我知道宜家應該點同另一半相處<br />\n<br />\n我唔會恨我既ex 但多謝你令我成長 成為更好既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我終於放低到 祝你同女朋友幸福 <br />\n亦多謝你放走我 令我搵到宜家咁好既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人會同我一樣<br />\n由恨到放下到感謝 <br />\n呢個過程好奇妙 好似覺得自己長大<br />\n其實放手放下係一件咁舒服既事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796f7ff9af78256ef578163eb9f314c690e4fb05","tid":2434404,"uid":369320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:33:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">閱</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"66aa56439c9f0765a8dd4362e5c22e2286a9bd48","tid":2434404,"uid":299433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"22ea7406340e32d62d654d8dcb63c950e95e9706","tid":2434404,"uid":300918,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"收皮啦收皮啦收皮啦"},{"pid":"d775eb78909f5bcdf17565a0a5bbdffd4f40f8a5","tid":2434404,"uid":364233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:34:51.000Z","msg":"對唔住"},{"pid":"a4ef3f92f4b814075c6abcc0d14cb3a1e846a927","tid":2434404,"uid":99700,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"分多幾次手成長得更快"},{"pid":"b66c579aa86642aa9f5c0cbd03877e4